17 defined in Section 748 of Title 21 of the Oklahoma Statutes;
18 2. “Private organization” means a nonprofit corporation
19 certified by the Office of the Attorney General that provides
20 support services to adult victims of human trafficking;
21 3. “Sexual trafficking” means human trafficking for commercial
22 sex as defined in Section 748 of Title 21 of the Oklahoma Statutes;
23 and
